annotationA: Vacuolar protein sorting 16A; It is involved in the biological process described with: regulation of SNARE complex assembly; eye pigment granule organization; endosomal transport; cellular response to starvation; lysosomal transport; negative regulation of Notch signaling pathway; endosome to lysosome transport; autophagic vacuole fusion; intracellular protein transport
annotationB: Protein ROP; May be a component of one of the vesicle trafficking pathways. May interact functionally with Ras2 protein
